data.description: OPEN HOUSES SAT & SUN, 12/2-12/3, 11am-3pm. Clean 3 Bedroom / 1 Bathroom home in North Bakersfield.  NOW AVAILABLE FOR SHOWINGS! Large Corner Lot w/ huge backyard.  Detached 2-Car Garage, Indoor Utility Room, Multiple Level Home w/ Large Bedroom below grade, Large Kitchen w/ Breakfast Nook, Newer Dual Pane Windows, Newer Roof & Insulation, Two sets of Solar Panels and a Water Softening System. New Exterior Paint, New Water Heater, One of the existing solar systems to be paid off prior to close of escrow.
